{
  "text": "Reverse Engineering is process that duplicates existing objects to see how it works [CITATION_1] . Nowadays, reverse engineering software package was applied into industrial process, such as using 3D scanner in computer aided inspection [CITATION_2] , analyzing FEM in aerospace turbine blade [CITATION_3] , and managing file system in CCTC [CITATION_4] .",
  "correct_citation": {
